'''三硫代亚砷酸钾'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为K<sub>3</sub>AsS<sub>3</sub>。

==制备==
三硫代亚砷酸钾可由[[三硫化二砷|三硫化二砷]]、金属[[钾|钾]]和[[硫|硫]]在液氨中按化学计量比反应得到：<ref name=mercouri>Mercouri G. Kanatzidis and Jun-Hong Chou. Isolation of β-Ag<sub>3</sub>AsSe<sub>3</sub> , (Me<sub>3</sub>NH)[Ag<sub>3</sub>As<sub>2</sub>Se<sub>5</sub>], K<sub>5</sub>Ag<sub>2</sub>As<sub>3</sub>Se<sub>9</sub> , and KAg<sub>3</sub>As<sub>2</sub>S<sub>5</sub> : Novel Solid State Silver Thio- and Selenoarsenates from Solvento-thermal Synthesis. ''Journal of Solid State Chemistry'', 1996. 127: 186-201</ref>
: 6 K + As<sub>2</sub>S<sub>3</sub> + 3 S → 2 K<sub>3</sub>AsS<sub>3</sub>
==性质==
它和氯化三羰基(五甲基环戊二烯)钼(II)<!-- CAS: 63511-23-9 -->反应，依据反应条件（温度、溶剂）不同，生成不同的产物，如[Cp<sup>*</sup><sub>2</sub>Mo<sub>2</sub>S<sub>4</sub>]（Cp<sup>*</sup>为五甲基环戊二烯）等。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of Organometallic Chemistry|volume=627|issue=2|language=en|date=2001-05|pages=139–143|doi=10.1016/S0022-328X(01)00709-4|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0022328X01007094|title=Dinuclear molybdenum complexes containing the novel μ,η1:3-AsS2 ligand: synthesis and molecular structure of [{Cp*2Mo2(CO)2As2S4}·2Cr(CO)5]·0.5CH2Cl2 (Cp*=C5Me5)|accessdate=2020-04-23|author=Henri Brunner, Franz Leis, Joachim Wachter, Manfred Zabel}}</ref>

它和[[氯化镍|氯化镍]]、[[四苯基溴化𬭸|四苯基溴化𬭸]]进行水热反应，能够得到配合物(Ph<sub>4</sub>P)<sub>2</sub>[NiAs<sub>4</sub>S<sub>8</sub>]。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=36|issue=1|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=1997-01|pages=4–9|doi=10.1021/ic951665i|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ic951665i|title=Synthesis and Characterization of (Ph 4 P) 2 [Ni 2 As 4 S 8 ], (Me 4 N) 2 [Mo 2 O 2 As 2 S 7 ], and (Et 4 N) 2 [Mo 2 O 2 As 2 Se 7 ]. New One-Dimensional Polymeric Compounds Containing Thio- and Selenoarsenate Ligands|accessdate=2020-04-23|author=Jun-Hong Chou, Jason A. Hanko, Mercouri G. Kanatzidis}}</ref>
